{"tid":2061864,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好將社會上受返黎嘅氣發洩落父母身上","createTime":"2020-06-12T16:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T15:58:53.000Z","uid":35662,"like":274,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7b00168b8cefeb62f9d8d0d8528922ba91a1f8","tid":2061864,"uid":35662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"喺香港呢個地方長大，好多人價值觀不知不覺被扭曲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼見人哋父母可以幫個仔女出錢出力，你會覺得自己父母比唔上人係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學業/工作/生活壓力大，你會覺得留喺屋企一無所知嘅父母嘅提點好煩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n父母被tvb新聞帶風向，你會好嬲覺得社會局面係由父母呢類人一手造成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但若果父母已經將你養大成人又唔會點逼你交家用，若果父母每次同你爭拗嘅出發點只係改善你嘅作息健康/你嘅個人手尾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你對父母把尺又可唔可以寬鬆啲呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「人類最大錯誤，對外人親切有禮，而對家人尖酸刻薄」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度覺得我講緊你嘅話，無錯我應該係講緊你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係個壞榜樣嘅仔，亦係個壞榜樣嘅呀哥，唔識處理你哋嘅衝突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係希望你唔好再衝動講出「關你撚事」「窮就當初咪生啦」「人哋父母XXX你XXX」之類嘅說話，試吓畀啲耐性同呀媽相處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望你睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b30eeef4098dc5942bb2dcb47b1a9d4f921268","tid":2061864,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df97574d1394e40e398d120af7d54fd2224809a6","tid":2061864,"uid":356218,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"好彩不嬲都孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e1bed887e4f6271b8dcd371e18b133295577d6","tid":2061864,"uid":247192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\